### Press Release Flow Test
# Test the press release intake flow with the staging assistant

@host = http://localhost:{{port}}
@phone = +1234567890

### 1. Start conversation
POST {{host}}/agent
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

From={{phone}}&Body=I want to create a press release

### 2. Provide announcement type
POST {{host}}/agent
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

From={{phone}}&Body=This is a funding announcement

### 3. Provide headline
POST {{host}}/agent
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

From={{phone}}&Body=TechCorp Raises $10M Series A to Transform Business Operations

### 4. Provide key facts
POST {{host}}/agent
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

From={{phone}}&Body=Company: TechCorp, Amount: $10 million, Date: Today, Lead Investor: Venture Partners, Use of funds: Product development and market expansion

### 5. Provide quotes
POST {{host}}/agent
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

From={{phone}}&Body=CEO John Smith: "We're thrilled to have Venture Partners leading our Series A round." Investor Jane Doe: "TechCorp's innovative approach to business automation made this an easy investment decision."

### 6. Provide boilerplate
POST {{host}}/agent
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

From={{phone}}&Body=TechCorp is a leading technology company specializing in AI-powered business automation solutions. Founded in 2020, the company serves over 500 enterprise clients worldwide.

### 7. Provide media contact
POST {{host}}/agent
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

From={{phone}}&Body=Sarah Johnson, sarah@techcorp.com, 555-123-4567

### 8. Confirm completion
POST {{host}}/agent
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

From={{phone}}&Body=OK

### 9. Reset session
POST {{host}}/agent
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

From={{phone}}&Body=reset